{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in-- well, we didn't stay together, because it was not good to stay together, for-- just my-- so we-- they stayed probably about a mile away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing is probably-- is probably the-- nothing is-- is probably the answer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But just like, delouse our self, if that's the right-- that's about the-- well, we were-- we were kept busy, you know, to keep clean.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To this guy for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not what-- no, I can't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he-- he didn't want to keep us no more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it was-- it was-- it was actually, if they catch you, they're going to shoot him with us, together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was anybody that saved somebody always, you know, his life was on the line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's not my best subject.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] P-A-W-L-O-S-K-I-- something like that, K-I, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a very poor farmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he had six kids himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think he had like, four acres of land.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And talked him in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And beside talking him in, he also-- we had some-- I don't know if it was money, or if it was just some cloth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he build us-- our-- a-- in-- in the barn, he build like a-- a-- another small floor, something, to keep us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he really hid it on top-- on top of the barn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He separated a-- he made a room out of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up above.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took us in, but he couldn't feed us, because really, he really was a very poor guy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then again, with the contacts my father had, so we used to go out once a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
